frames.caption: A majestic tiger stands on a rocky ledge, gazing forward as a hawk swoops down nearby. The scene is set against a backdrop of towering cliffs and a sky filled with fluffy clouds.
frames.description: The image depicts a dramatic interaction between a tiger and a hawk in a natural setting. The tiger stands confidently on a rocky outcrop, while the hawk appears to be in mid-flight, creating a dynamic and tense atmosphere.

frames.caption: A majestic creature with the body of a tiger and large, powerful wings soars through a lush canyon. The vibrant orange and black stripes of the tiger contrast with the deep green foliage and towering cliffs. The scene captures a sense of wonder and fantasy as the creature glides gracefully through the air.
frames.description: The image depicts a fantastical scene where a winged tiger is flying through a verdant canyon. The setting is a lush, natural environment with towering cliffs and dense greenery, creating a mystical atmosphere.
